<item>
            <title>[FLINK-24903] AdaptiveSchedulerTest.testJobStatusListenerNotifiedOfJobStatusChanges unstable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-24903</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://dev.azure.com/khachatryanroman/flink/_build/results?buildId=1225&amp;amp;view=logs&amp;amp;j=9dc1b5dc-bcfa-5f83-eaa7-0cb181ddc267&amp;amp;t=511d2595-ec54-5ab7-86ce-92f328796f20&amp;amp;l=7753&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://dev.azure.com/khachatryanroman/flink/_build/results?buildId=1225&amp;amp;view=logs&amp;amp;j=9dc1b5dc-bcfa-5f83-eaa7-0cb181ddc267&amp;amp;t=511d2595-ec54-5ab7-86ce-92f328796f20&amp;amp;l=7753&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
 2021-11-14T20:22:23.1142812Z Nov 14 20:22:23 [ERROR] Failures:
 2021-11-14T20:22:23.1149388Z Nov 14 20:22:23 [ERROR]   AdaptiveSchedulerTest.testJobStatusListenerNotifiedOfJobStatusChanges:684
 2021-11-14T20:22:23.1150058Z Nov 14 20:22:23 Expected: (a collection containing &amp;lt;RUNNING&amp;gt; and a collection containing &amp;lt;FINISHED&amp;gt;)
 2021-11-14T20:22:23.1150581Z Nov 14 20:22:23      but: a collection containing &amp;lt;FINISHED&amp;gt; was &amp;lt;RUNNING&amp;gt;
 2021-11-14T20:22:23.1152966Z Nov 14 20:22:23 [INFO]
 2021-11-14T20:22:23.1156414Z Nov 14 20:22:23 [ERROR] Tests run: 6048, Failures: 1, Errors: 0, Skipped: 97
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Locally, it fails ~14 runs out of 100 (when running only testJobStatusListenerNotifiedOfJobStatusChanges in a loop).&lt;br/&gt;
Also on master.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;It looks like job termination future is always completed before the jobStatusChangeListener is notified (AdaptiveScheduler.transitionToState, targetState.getState() completes the future).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sleeping for 1ms before checking the assertion prevents the failure.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;cc: &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=trohrmann&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;trohrmann&quot;&gt;trohrmann&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
